<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00">其实啊，<delay8 />我向<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />借了个东西，
到现在还没有还回去呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想不到<delay8 />我竟然会犯这种糊涂。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />事到如今，<delay8 />
我还有什么脸面<delay8 />把东西拿去物归原主啊。<delay20 />
唉～<delay8 />真是伤脑筋<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我替你还回去吧？</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老老实实去道歉吧</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前一阵子<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />来我家做客，<delay8 />
回去的时候，<delay8 />
把东西落在我家了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话虽如此，<delay8 />
我有点事情需要处理，<delay8 />
没有时间送过去啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />
虽然很不好意思，<delay8 />不过能麻烦你替我<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那跑一趟吗？</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你自己去吧</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前一阵子，<delay8 />
有个寄给<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的包裹，
不知为何<delay8 />被送到我家来了。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在正在忙别的事情，<delay8 />
一直找不到机会把东西拿去物归原主啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />继续把东西留在我这也不是个办法<tag a="110" b="0" />
真令人伤脑筋啊。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我替你送过去</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之后再去吧</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不好意思啊，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />
那就拜托你咯！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啊，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />
那这东西就交给你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你愿意帮忙送过去吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那这东西就拜托你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
你说得没错，<delay8 />
这种时候就应该老老实实去道歉。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
明明是忘在我家的东西<delay8 />却让你送过去，<delay8 />
于情于理好像都不太合适啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
