<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这东西就由我自己送过去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没办法，<delay8 />
虽然得让那家伙等上一会儿，<delay8 />
但我也是情非得已啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等我把事情处理完，<delay8 />
再火速送过去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay8 />
我有点事情想找你商量一下，<delay8 />
你能听我说说吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />我想请你帮忙
把一个东西交给<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么说呢，<delay8 />因为我平时倍受关照，
所以就<delay20 />准备了一点谢礼。
但一到要送出手时，<delay8 />又感觉怪不好意思的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我替你送过去！</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油啊！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
你听我说！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实<delay8 />我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />
发生了一点争执<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />主要错在我太不成熟，<delay8 />没忍住发了火。<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又觉得特别尴尬，
一直没能去道歉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得至少得把这赔罪的礼物送过去才行，<delay8 />
到底<delay8 />该怎么办呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我替你送过去！</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油啊！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么？！<delay8 />真的吗？<delay20 />
