	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说得对，<delay8 />
这种东西还是得要自己亲手交给对方。<delay8 />
才能表现出诚意啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
谢谢你点醒了我啊！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好嘞！
听到你这么说，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感觉突然又鼓起勇气来了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
多亏你提点，<delay8 />我应该能好好
向<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />道歉了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然这样催促你有点不好意思，<delay8 />
