	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啊，<delay8 />就有劳你把<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的失物<delay8 />
